WEBVTT

00:00:01.280 --> 00:00:03.301
Kupata elimu ya chuo

00:00:03.325 --> 00:00:05.480
ni uwekezaji wa miaka 20

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:08.055
Unapokulia katika umaskini,

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:11.016
unakuwa hujazoea 
kufikiria mbele kiasi hicho

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:14.186
Badala yake, 
unafikiria wapi utapata mlo unaofuata

00:00:14.190 --> 00:00:17.256
na namna gani familia yako 
italipa kodi ya pango kwa mwezi huo

00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:20.416
Mbali na hilo, 
wazazi wangu na wazazi wa rafiki zangu

00:00:20.440 --> 00:00:24.840
walionekana kuwa vizuri tu wakiendesha 
teksi na kufanya kazi za usafi na uhudumu.

00:00:24.920 --> 00:00:26.816
Ni mpaka nilipokuwa kijana

00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:29.320
nilipogundua sikutaka kufanya kazi zile.